deck: Elle(s). There are two of them. No doubt, once you've met them . Elle(s). Your friends, or maybe more... Elle(s). Those whom we love and who consider ideal. Elle(s). Those 18 years old. As to us.
name: Elle(s)

description: Since her creation in 1962, Sabrina the Teenage Witch has become one of the most popular and endearing characters in American pop culture. To celebrate her 50-year anniversary, Archie Comics presents 50 of Sabrina's most spellbinding stories! This Digital Exclusive collects OVER 350 PAGES of content spanning Sabrina's history, including a NEVER-BEFORE-SEEN origin story, written by Sabrina creator George Gladir himself. So join Sabrina, Salem, Aunties Hilda and Zelda, and many more for the most magical book of the year!
name: Sabrina the Teenage Witch 50 Magical Stories

description: It's an alien invasion! Join America's favorite teenage earthlings in some interplanetary fun. Are these galactic visitors friendly, or do they want to conquer the world? This 112 page Digital Exclusive collects some of the most out-of-this-world stories ever printed and features appearances by Sabrina, Little Archie, Li'l Jinx, and more!
name: Archie's Close Encounters

description: Cast your vote for Class President of Riverdale High! This 118 page Digital Exclusive collects some of Archie & the gang's best political rivalry stories. Will Archie get to ride on Air Force Fun? Will Betty or Veronica win the highest office in the land? Or are they all a bunch of lame ducks? This bipartisan book has all the answers!
name: Archie's Campaign Trail

description: Anything boys can do, girls can do better! The gals are taking center stage and showing the boys who's boss! Watch the girls as they challenge their male counterparts to a dance-off, show them what's what on the sports field and even fight crime! It's not just a battle of the sexes, but also a fun walk through history, highlighting important female figures throughout time, standing up for what's right! This 100+ page digital exclusive features the lovely ladies of Riverdale, including Betty, Veronica, Nancy, Cheryl, Ethel, Ginger, Trula Twyst and Brigitte! In this collection, the girls really do rule!
name: B&V Friends Girls Rule!

description: Grab your wallets, it's time for a SHOPPING SPREE!
name: Betty & Veronica $hopping $pree!

description: What happens when Archie and the gang get tangled up with the most fearsome creatures of the night? Things get a little batty! Join the Riverdale gang in some stories that you can really sink your fangs into. Whether you're a Twi-hard or like to kick it old-school with Dracula, this book's got you covered. With over 100 pages of bloody good stories, this book has more laughs than you can count!
name: Archie The Vampire Saga

description: It's Jughead's dog, HOT DOG! What's that scamp up to now?
name: Jughead's Pal Hot Dog

description:
They say a great nose is the banner of a great man?look no further than Jughead Jones! When the new drama teacher at Riverdale High puts on a production of the famous play Cyrano de Bergerac, Jughead is unwillingly cast as the titular character! While studying his part, he falls asleep, and dreams that he really is Cyrano! Can Jughead steal the show, even in his wildest dreams? Who nose?!

Enjoy the complete story, taken from the pages of Jughead Double Digest #165-168!
name: Jughead As Cyrano Jones

description:
This Digital Exclusive features over 100 pages of content, including an appearance from the pin-up queen, Katy Keene!

How could Betty and Veronica get any better? Why, with New Year's Resolutions, of course! Join the girls and their friends as they make resolutions for the new year. The real question, though, is if they can keep them! Is Betty finally through with Archie? Can Veronica keep her nose out of other people's business? And could Archie possibly keep his resolution to not date Betty and Veronica on the same day?! You'll have to read to find out!
name: Betty & Veronica New Year's Resolutions!

description: This Digital Exclusive collects 100 PAGES of fan-favorite, Archie 3000! Travel to the 31st Century with Archie and his friends! In the year 3000, Riverdale is home to hoverboards, intergalactic travel, alien life, and everyone's favorite space case, Archie! Follow the gang as they encounter detention robots, teleporters, wacky fashion trends, and much more. Will the teens of the future get in as much trouble as the ones from our time? Find out with 100 pages of exciting stories!
name: Archie 3000! Teen of the Future

description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 150 PAGES of content, including a special appearance by Sabrina the Teenage Witch! Love is in the air in Riverdale! Archie, Betty, Veronica, and the whole gang have been struck by Cupid's arrow, and you can join in the fun with this oversized Digital Exclusive! Read on to see if Archie can juggle his Valentine's Day dates. Will Reggie and Cheryl create a love connection? And if Ethel isn't giving Jughead boxes of chocolates, who is?! With over 150 pages of content, you'll LOVE this digital-only special!
name: Archie's Sweet Hearts

description: This Digital Exclusive features 50 PAGES of Archie's wackiest movie adventures! Lights! Camera! Action! Archie and friends are on the SMALL screen in this 50-page Digital Exclusive, spotlighting some of our blockbuster movie stories. Whether they're behind the camera or in front of it, Archie, Betty, Veronica, Jughead and the whole gang always get two thumbs up! So curl up with a bucket of popcorn and enjoy the show!
name: Archie & Friends Movie Magic

description:
This Digital Exclusive collects 100 pages of Jughead's best slacker stories!

When the going gets tough, Jughead gets going-to the nearest couch! School is in session, and Riverdale's laziest teenager is ready to give you the ultimate guide to goofing off. Learn how to nap correctly, how to avoid work, how to bum money off your friends, and more! Settle down and check out 100 pages of Jughead's laziest (and funniest) moments!
name: Jughead Slacker University

description: Once upon a time, in the little town of Riverdale, girl-next-door Betty Cooper was the best storyteller of all! Check out Betty's favorite fairy tales and bedtime stories in this 100-page Digital Exclusive. Take a trip to the Land of Ooze and meet a weird Wizard! See some classic nursery rhymes get madcap modern updates! And could that lowly frog be the Prince that Betty's always dreamed of?! Read on, fairest reader of them all, and live happily ever after! This Digital Exclusive features 100 PAGES of funny fables, nursery rhymes, and fairy tales!
name: Betty's Story Time

description:
This Digital Exclusive collects OVER 150 PAGES of out-of-this-world content!

Take a ride in a flying saucer with Cosmo the Merry Martian! For the first time ever, this classic interplanetary tale has been collected into one giant-size collection. Join Cosmo, Orbi, Astra, and all their wacky friends as they explore the unknown and discover all-new life forms. What adventures will these Martian explorers find on Jupiter, or Venus, or even Earth?! Put on your spacesuit and find out!
name: Cosmo The Merry Martian The Complete Series

description: It's time for mischief and mayhem! Li'l Jinx is a feisty little girl ready to stir up trouble. Join Li'l Jinx and her friends Charley, Greg, Russ, and more as they live life to the fullest! Can her poor father keep up with her? Find out with 150 pages of classic Li'l Jinx, and a special sneak preview of Jinx: Little Miss Steps, her new graphic novel-where she's not so li'l anymore!
name: Li'l Jinx

description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 140 PAGES of family fun! How did the kids from Riverdale High get to be so quirky, wacky, and fun? Judging by their families, it might be genetic! Join Archie, Betty, Veronica, and the whole gang as they hang out with their parents, cousins, siblings, and more. This Digital Exclusive features more than 15 stories about characters like Betty's seldom seen brother Chic, Veronica's bratty cousin Leroy, Coach Clayton, Raj Patel's family, and even Ms. Beazly's daughter! So settle down at the dinner table and celebrate family with Archie & Friends!
name: Archie & Friends Family Values

description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 300 PAGES of content! Watch out, Archie -- that red-hot seductress, Cheryl Blossom, is back in a big way! By popular demand, we've collected some of the best Cheryl stories of all time in this digital-only extravaganza! From her first appearance in 1982, this beautiful billionaire has caused trouble for the Riverdale gang with her rotten brother, Jason. Go bonkers for Blossom with over 300 pages of content from superstar creators like Dan DeCarlo, Frank Doyle, Dan Parent and more!
name: The Best of Cheryl Blossom

description:
Four Wolves on the Road to Paradise

Humans thought the wolves died off two centuries ago in this bleak post-apocalyptic wasteland. But some survivors lurk among the humans by mentally cloaking their animal bodies. One white wolf, Kiba, scours the land for the scent of the Lunar Flower that will lead them all to Paradise...
name: Volume 1

description:
Four Wolves on the Run From Mankind

Kiba's pack of wolves answers the highest, most dire calling--they seek the legendary Paradise.

They have tracked down the Lunar Flower, and together, they continue their pilgrimage with the armies of humanity at their tails. But will the scent of the Lunar Flower lead them to Paradise or a deadly false legend?

The drama reaches its climax in this final volume!
name: Volume 2
